Package: aocseq
Type: Package
Title: A package designed for the analysis of single cell RNA sequencing data, can be used to model gene expression changes caused by the activation of cells.
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Mae Woods, Noah Crooks
Maintainer: <mae.woods@bcm.edu>
Description: Software initially developed to process data of the activation of cells and sequencing. 
License: BSD2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
